      "side": 1,
      "message": "That sounds like related work rather than this CL. SVG filter painting was recently (a bit over week ago now I think) changed to paint in the same way as HTML filters. In an interim the bounds for the associated saveLayer() will be too large (using a conservative estimate based on the filter region), which could be what you\u0027re observing (there are Chromium perf tests that also noticed). I just published a CL with the updated bounds computation (it was blocked on this change).\nIf you can point me to the original SVG file I can check what it does.",
